### 1. Get all tariffs (should be empty or show your test tariff)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs

### 2. Create new tariff
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Premium WiFi",
  "downloadMbps": 100,
  "uploadMbps": 50,
  "durationHours": 24,
  "maxDevices": 5,
  "basePrice": 19.99,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "billingType": "ONE_TIME"
}

### 3. Get tariff by ID (use ID from step 2 response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1

### 4. Update tariff (use ID from step 2)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Premium WiFi",
  "downloadMbps": 150,
  "uploadMbps": 75,
  "durationHours": 48,
  "maxDevices": 8,
  "basePrice": 29.99,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "billingType": "ONE_TIME"
}

### 5. Get updated tariff to verify changes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1

### 6. Delete tariff
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1

### 7. Verify deletion (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1